{"tid":1919021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［補刀？！］英國26個保守黨員聯署 反對政府用華為；香港人交反抗爭資料時，應該包埋港共既監控、俾資料國安既行為？！","createTime":"2020-03-10T13:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T01:52:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69e1c3f1485c1d82d63c16951d603801abac63e9","tid":1919021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7QzefH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7QzefH.png&h=03cb44a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/owenpaterson/status/1237313936653012993?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fowenpaterson%2Fstatus%2F1237313936653012993%3Fs%3D21&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=c3c9176b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fowenpaterson%2Fstatus%2F1237313936653012993%3Fs%3D21&h=02856a43\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/owenpaterson/status/1237313936653012993?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日：<br />\nBoris Johnson is facing his first major Commons rebellion as a group of senior Conservatives mount a bid to ban Huawei from the UK&rsquo;s 5G infrastructure by 2022.<br />\n<br />\nFormer Tory leader Sir Iain Duncan Smith and a group of senior MPs have tabled an amendment to legislation due in parliament on Tuesday, which would lock out &ldquo;high-risk vendors&rdquo; such as Huawei from the network by the end of 2022.<br />\n<br />\nWhile Mr Johnson commands an 80-strong majority, the group &ndash; which includes former cabinet ministers David Davis, Damian Green and Owen Paterson &ndash; expects dozens of Tories to back it, potentially inflicting a defeat on the government.<br />\n<br />\nIt comes after the prime minister enraged critics of the Chinese telecoms giant by allowing the firm to build parts of the UK&rsquo;s 5G network. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-huawei-5g-decision-trump-tories-a9380561.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fpolitics%2Fboris-johnson-huawei-5g-decision-trump-tories-a9380561.html&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=bc95c28e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-huawei-5g-decision-trump-tories-a9380561.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我記得有幾單俾狗查完<br />\n過關時俾公安拘留既事件？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7271cfa90247bfb4e8703ea3ed19b2f186ef701d","tid":1919021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc38094d73fd7c024510f992ed397c991eb90138","tid":1919021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb0bca6ce0c48024f870e0129a836a846c62420","tid":1919021,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ec7bd3dbeaf193d5f17239d35f774434c8ddc63","tid":1919021,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"英國華為事件未完"},{"pid":"dfb065aab868b94dbda3f2f16a22f3bbe1c6afb6","tid":1919021,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"ok 喎 交咗先算"},{"pid":"ed81dea13b49799c621803aee0ac40428aa767da","tid":1919021,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfb065aab868b94dbda3f2f16a22f3bbe1c6afb6","tid":1919021,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"ok 喎 交咗先算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:00:13.000Z","msg":